rows.label: bf06500100_0030
rows.name:
Warned ya, didn't we? You mess with
Thunderbolt Zeke, that's whatcha get.

rows.label: bf06500100_0060
rows.name:
Anyway, this has gone on long enough.
Nighty night, chaps.

rows.label: bf06500100_0070
rows.name: Very much looking forward to interrogating you later!

rows.label: bf06500100_0080
rows.name:
Here I go!
Bringer of Chao-

rows.label: bf06500100_0110
rows.name:
Seems they don't call you "Thunderbolt" for nothing.
That's the first time I've ever missed a vital point...

rows.label: bf06500100_0150
rows.name:
Don't worry yourself...
It's just a scratch, really...

rows.label: bf06500100_0170
rows.name: Relax, he's not made of glass.

rows.label: bf06500100_0190
rows.name: Don't mind me, I'm just a spectator.

rows.label: bf06500100_0200
rows.name: He, on the other hand, insisted on coming here...

rows.label: bf06500100_0220
rows.name:
Correct.
I will be taking both the Sanctus Chain and the Holy Grail.

rows.label: bf06500100_0230
rows.name:
You just try and take 'em!
I know you're strong...

rows.label: bf06500100_0240
rows.name: but there's no way we're giving you Homura or Hikari!

rows.label: bf06500100_0250
rows.name: Strong words. But words do little.

rows.label: bf06500100_0260
rows.name: If you know what you desire, you will have to show it...

rows.label: bf06500100_0265
rows.name: not with words, but with your own strength!

rows.label: bf06500100_0290
rows.name: There no change to ether energy of surroundings.

rows.label: bf06500100_0300
rows.name:
That energy being emitted from
interior of body.

rows.label: bf06500100_0310
rows.name:
Just like our Homura, then?
Where do they even keep all that energy?

rows.label: bf06500100_0320
rows.name:
How about all that rage energy he's got
all pent up inside?
